{
  "texts": [
    "The single cell colonies were screened by T7 Endonuclease I (T7E1, New England Biolabs, Ipswich, USA, Cat#M0302L) assay, and the Sanger sequencing (Eurofins) results were analyzed with the TIDE webtool 57.",
    "The A-tailing PCR products from the candidate clones were cloned into the pGEM-T vector (Promega, Madison, USA, Cat#A3600) and sequenced.",
    "Then two clones from each mutation combination were selected and further validated by western blotting.",
    "In brief, the protein lysis from the iPSCs was electrophoresed and transferred onto 0.2 μm PVDF membranes.",
    "The membranes were blocked with 5% non-fat milk for one hour at room temperature (RT) and incubated with primary antibodies overnight at 4 °C with shaking."
  ]
}